    JoinOperator<I1,I2,OUT>

    @Public
public static final class JoinOperator.JoinOperatorSets<I1,I2>
extends JoinOperatorSetsBase<I1,I2>
    Intermediate step of a Join transformation.
    To continue the Join transformation, select the join key of the first input DataSet by calling where(int...) or where(org.apache.flink.api.java.functions.KeySelector).

      • where

        public JoinOperator.JoinOperatorSets.JoinOperatorSetsPredicate where(int... fields)
        Continues a Join transformation.
        Defines the Tuple fields of the first join DataSet that should be used as join keys.
        Note: Fields can only be selected as join keys on Tuple DataSets.
        覆盖:
        where 在类中 JoinOperatorSetsBase<I1,I2>
        参数:
        fields - The indexes of the other Tuple fields of the first join DataSets that should be used as keys.
        返回:
        An incomplete Join transformation. Call JoinOperator.JoinOperatorSets.JoinOperatorSetsPredicate.equalTo(int...) or JoinOperator.JoinOperatorSets.JoinOperatorSetsPredicate.equalTo(KeySelector) to continue the Join.
        另请参阅:
        Tuple, DataSet

      • where

        public JoinOperator.JoinOperatorSets.JoinOperatorSetsPredicate where(String... fields)
        Continues a Join transformation.
        Defines the fields of the first join DataSet that should be used as grouping keys. Fields are the names of member fields of the underlying type of the data set.
        覆盖:
        where 在类中 JoinOperatorSetsBase<I1,I2>
        参数:
        fields - The fields of the first join DataSets that should be used as keys.
        返回:
        An incomplete Join transformation. Call JoinOperator.JoinOperatorSets.JoinOperatorSetsPredicate.equalTo(int...) or JoinOperator.JoinOperatorSets.JoinOperatorSetsPredicate.equalTo(KeySelector) to continue the Join.
        另请参阅:
        Tuple, DataSet

      • where

        public <K> JoinOperator.JoinOperatorSets.JoinOperatorSetsPredicate where(org.apache.flink.api.java.functions.KeySelector<I1,K> keySelector)
        Continues a Join transformation and defines a KeySelector function for the first join DataSet.
        The KeySelector function is called for each element of the first DataSet and extracts a single key value on which the DataSet is joined.
        覆盖:
        where 在类中 JoinOperatorSetsBase<I1,I2>
        参数:
        keySelector - The KeySelector function which extracts the key values from the DataSet on which it is joined.
        返回:
        An incomplete Join transformation. Call JoinOperator.JoinOperatorSets.JoinOperatorSetsPredicate.equalTo(int...) or JoinOperator.JoinOperatorSets.JoinOperatorSetsPredicate.equalTo(KeySelector) to continue the Join.
        另请参阅:
        KeySelector, DataSet
